title: PhenolicsDB: PhenolicsDB: phenolics MS/MS (LC-ESI-QTOF) database repository — PhenolicsDB-package
text: Raw MS/MS data set authentic phenolics standards, including, phenolic acids, flavonoids, dihydrochalcones, carbohydrates. Standards collected using Agilent QTOF 6545 6546, negative positive polarities, 20 40 eV (CE). Standards collected using 6546 QTOF also contains MS/MS data 60 80 eV (CE). raw MS/MS files used jointly MS2extract package create -house MS/MS libaries.
